description:
Joel Lwaga - Olodumare  (Official Lyric Video)

Produced by : ​⁠@allanepyuza 
Song written by @joellwaga 

Presenting "Olodumare", a powerful and uplifting Gospel track by Joel Lwaga, produced by Allan Edward Pyuza. With deeply inspiring lyrics, Joel celebrates God's unwavering support, protection, and grace in this soul-stirring song.

Through its heartfelt melodies and meaningful message, "Olodumare" reminds us of faith, resilience, and the comforting truth that God is always in control—no matter the challenges we face. 

Release Date: October 11, 2024

Be inspired, share the message, and let this song move your heart! 

#JoelLwaga #Olodumare #AfroGospel
